   7:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   * @brief   CMSIS Cortex-M4 Device Peripheral Access Layer System Source File.
   8:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *
   9:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *   This file provides two functions and one global variable to be called from 
  10:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *   user application:
  11:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *      - SystemInit(): This function is called at startup just after reset and 
  12:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                      before branch to main program. This call is made inside
  13:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                      the "startup_stm32f4xx.s" file.
  14:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *
  15:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *      - SystemCoreClock variable: Contains the core clock (HCLK), it can be used
  16:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                  by the user application to setup the SysTick 
  17:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                  timer or configure other parameters.
  18:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                     
  19:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *      - SystemCoreClockUpdate(): Updates the variable SystemCoreClock and must
  20:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                 be called whenever the core clock is changed
  21:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *                                 during program execution.
  22:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *
  23:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   *
  24:../common/cmsis/device/system_stm32f4xx.c ****   ******************************************************************************
